      "tasks": {
        "plan": {
          "name": "plan",
          "instruction": "根据 goal 编写实现计划。计划必须包含:\n1. 实现步骤（bite-sized 为佳）\n2. 涉及的文件列表\n3. 测试策略\n4. 风险点\n5. 停止规则\n",
          "role": "planner",
          "inputs": [
            "goal",
            "project_context"
          ],
          "output": "plan_doc",
          "description": "",
          "timeout_seconds": 3600,
          "allowed_decisions": [
            "done",
            "fail",
            "blocked"
          ]
        },
        "review_plan": {
          "name": "review_plan",
          "instruction": "审查实现计划。从以下维度评估:\n1. 完整性 — 是否覆盖所有功能点\n2. 正确性 — 技术方案是否可行\n3. 测试覆盖 — 是否定义了足够的测试\n4. 风险 — 是否识别了关键风险\n5. 复杂度 — 是否可以简化\n\n输出 approve（可以执行）、revise（需要修改）或 reject（不可行）。\n",
          "role": "reviewer",
          "inputs": [
            "plan_doc",
            "project_context"
          ],
          "output": "review_doc",
          "description": "",
          "timeout_seconds": 3600,
          "allowed_decisions": [
            "approve",
            "revise",
            "reject"
          ]
        },
        "revise_plan": {
          "name": "revise_plan",
          "instruction": "根据审查意见修改实现计划。必须逐条回应审查意见，\n说明哪些采纳、哪些不采纳及原因。\n",
          "role": "planner",
          "inputs": [
            "plan_doc",
            "review_doc",
            "revision_instructions"
          ],
          "output": "plan_doc",
          "description": "",
          "timeout_seconds": 3600,
          "allowed_decisions": [
            "done",
            "fail",
            "blocked"
          ]
        },
        "execute": {
          "name": "execute",
          "instruction": "按照已批准的实现计划执行代码变更。\n严格按照计划步骤进行，不要跳过验证步骤。\n如果计划在执行中发现问题，输出 blocked 并说明原因。\n",
          "role": "executor",
          "inputs": [
            "plan_doc",
            "project_context"
          ],
          "output": "execution_report",
          "description": "",
          "timeout_seconds": 3600,
          "allowed_decisions": [
            "done",
            "fail",
            "blocked"
          ]
        },
        "audit": {
          "name": "audit",
          "instruction": "审计代码变更。检查:\n1. 是否按照计划执行\n2. 代码质量和风格\n3. 测试通过\n4. 无安全/性能问题\n5. 边界情况覆盖\n\n输出 approve（通过）、revise（需要修改）或 reject（不可接受）。\n",
          "role": "auditor",
          "inputs": [
            "plan_doc",
            "execution_report",
            "diff"
          ],
          "output": "audit_report",
          "description": "",
          "timeout_seconds": 3600,
          "allowed_decisions": [
            "approve",
            "revise",
            "reject"
          ]
        },
